title: [Sylvarraend, Wooded Trail]
description: The trail winds around a small pond overhung with moss-draped oaks.  Resting quietly on the moonlit surface of the pond, several ducks have tucked heads beneath wings for the night.
The trail winds around a small pond overhung with moss-draped oaks.  Several ducks float about the pond, occasionally ducking their heads beneath to fish for dinner.
